---
title: Pork Katsu & Garlic Rice with Ponzu Cucumber & Garlicky Greens
description: The warm tartness with notes of sweet will pop in your mouth and it’s all thanks to this katsu sauce poured over
crumbed pork. It’s a balance of flavours, from garlicky greens to ponzu soaked cucumber but they’re walking that
tightrope with ease. It deserves a round of applause.
